description:
Add 4 new tracks to GUNVOLT RECORDS: Cychronicle, including a brand new track from Luxia and a new track from Lumen's 3rd album!
Purchase this pack to add the following 4 songs to the game:
　・Nebulous Clock
　・Iolite
　・Paradox Stage
　・Afsān
name: GUNVOLT RECORDS Cychronicle Song Pack 6 Lumen & Luxia: ♪Nebulous Clock ♪Iolite ♪Paradox Stage ♪Afsān
